directions: ["Thaw bread dough or mix box dough for pizza crust.", "Spread on greased cookie sheet (like for a pizza).", "Mix next 7 ingredients and spread on dough.", "Cover with toppings you want; roll like a jelly roll.", "Place seam side down and brush with egg white.", "Bake at 350\u00b0 for 30 to 40 minutes."]

title: Coffee Cake
ingredients: ["1 c. shortening (half butter or oleo)", "1 c. brown sugar, packed", "1 c. white sugar", "2 c. flour", "2 eggs", "1 tsp. soda", "1/2 tsp. salt", "1 c. yogurt or sour cream"]
directions: ["Cream shortening and sugars in a large mixing bowl.", "Add flour and crumble together.", "Set aside 1 cup of this mixture.", "Mix eggs, salt, soda and yogurt together in small mixing bowl.", "Add this to the sugar mixture and combine (seems better if not completely smooth) and pour into a greased and floured 9 x 13 x 2-inch pan. Bake about 40 minutes at 350\u00b0."]

title: Chocolate Cinnamon Cake
ingredients: ["2 c. flour", "2 c. sugar", "4 Tbsp. cocoa", "1 c. cold water", "1 stick oleo", "1/2 c. shortening", "2 eggs, slightly beaten", "1/2 c. buttermilk", "1 tsp. each: soda, cinnamon and vanilla"]
directions: ["Sift in large mixing bowl the flour and sugar.", "In a saucepan, put cocoa, cold water, oleo and shortening.", "Bring to a boil. Pour over flour and sugar; add eggs, buttermilk, soda, cinnamon and vanilla.", "Bake in large 11 x 17-inch pan at 350\u00b0 for 20 minutes or less."]
